Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji who was being pressed \Ninto a marriage and left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom became furious after learning \NCracker, one of the Sweet 3 Generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,got taken down by Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To avenge him,\NShe deployed an enraged army on Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy didn't retreat from the spot\Nwhere he decided to wait for Sanji{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he faced the enraged army\Ngathering all his strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Sanji was with Pudding...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my... salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm good enough for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get married tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy keeps fighting\Nwithout knowing Sanji's decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'll Wait Here!\NLuffy vs. the Enraged Army!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,IN THE OUTSKIRTS OF SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go anywhere!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already reached his limit! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't create big thunderclouds like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can use Big Mom's thunderclouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that a girl like you could\Nmake such a big lightning strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Famous Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shirauo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think-{\i1}ju{\i0}!\NWe didn't mean to change sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amande-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow Ballad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you're going to kill \Nme, d-do it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless killing someone quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut at the most painful \Nand tormenting speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem like\Nhe was fighting Big Bro Cracker all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chess Peacekeepers aren't that weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he tear them to pieces like trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cream Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,MIRRO-WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting, reindeer!\NYou became muscular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's do it, Carrot!\N--Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This reindeer's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run over and kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rabbit can fight too! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should I do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.\NThat's not gonna happen, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:12:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the World of Books!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:14:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cream Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one more-{\i1}fa{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:16.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:17:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to marry Pudding-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to let my friends go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to reasonable deals,\NI can be reasonable myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let all members of the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are your friends for now \Nleave this island alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop the idea of running away\Nand marry without resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn a blind eye to everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it!\NI'll make Pudding-{\i1}chan{\i0} happy at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're so in love with my daughter!\NI'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that the Straw Hats have done to me\Nare normally inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They destroyed the maze-like forest\Nand took down one of our Sweet Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:19:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, at the Fish-Man Island,\Nnot only did they eat my candies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they also picked a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the top priority is \Nyou and Pudding's marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things go well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about this time tomorrow,\NI'll gain Germa's military strength
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll all have a delicious wedding cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't run away,\Neverything will turn out for the best, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got him.\NHe gave us a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We avenged our big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kingbaum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why the Chess Peacekeepers, \Nwho are Homies, couldn't fight like usual
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how you guys could \Nmake it out of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have Mama's Vivre Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Lola."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lola?! Did you steal it from her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! That runaway girl got killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lola!\N--What were her last words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!\NShe's my friend! She gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Mama that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately,\Nwe were ordered to catch you guys alive. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the Chess Peacekeepers \Nhave been beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... wait... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:14.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Nami have been \Ncaptured in an inescapable cell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,in a book kept deep inside \Nthe Emperor's chateau!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:21.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Brook and Pedro are trying\Nto sneak past
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:23.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet General Smoothie and heavy security{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in order to perform an \Nunprecedented safecracking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Invading the Chateau! \NReach the Road Ponegliff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
